<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Vozmia | Developers</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>

  <link href="/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
  
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kdam+Thmor+Pro&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-gray-800">
  <!-- Header -->
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <!-- Main Section -->
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">About the Developer</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Hi, I'm Jorge Garcia-Zapata, the developer behind Vozmia. I'm a full-stack engineer passionate about creating human-centered AI tools. Vozmia is built to reduce AI hallucinations by letting real business owners provide correct answers. These answers help our AI learn like a babyâ€”through context, clarity, and feedback.</p>
      <p class="mb-2">You can view my full resume <a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NDikWpI8EaFG7o0wMfvaF8rMVqbEv8DF/view?usp=sharing" class="text-blue-600 underline">here</a>.</p>
      <p>Connect with me on <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jorgeagarcia1/" class="text-blue-600 underline">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">What is Vozmia?</h2>
      <p>Vozmia is an AI-ready business index that allows owners to contribute correct information and reduce misleading chatbot answers. By empowering small businesses to directly guide AI, we're making conversational search more accurate and community-driven.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Want to Collaborate?</h2>
      <form action="/developers/contact" method="POST" class="space-y-4 p-6 rounded border border-gray-300">
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Full Name" required class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" required class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded">
        <textarea name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Your message or idea..." required class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="bg-yellow-500 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded hover:bg-yellow-600">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script type="module" src="/js/dropdown.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
